            					<figure>
                                    <img src='https://www.theparisreview.org//blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/782bd48e-153b-64b9-3331-edb8c5a698c6-scaled.jpg'
                                        srcset='https://www.theparisreview.org//blog/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/782bd48e-153b-64b9-3331-edb8c5a698c6-scaled.jpg 1000w,
